---
import BaseHead from '../components/BaseHead.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import { SITE_TITLE, SITE_DESCRIPTION } from '../consts';
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
	<head>
		<BaseHead title={SITE_TITLE} description={SITE_DESCRIPTION} />
	</head>
	<body>
		<Header />
		<main>
			<h1>Hello, I'm Lorenzo</h1>
			<p>
				I'm a backend developer from Milano with Italian-Cuban heritage. I build systems 
				and write code, but I also create music under the alias 
				<a href="https://open.spotify.com/intl-it/artist/1tzPTUM1XKUck2s6TUh2o1">AcjnN</a>.
			</p>
			<p>
				My professional work focuses on backend development and infrastructure architecture. 
				Musically, I've been playing piano since childhood, later picking up guitar, 
				drums, and bass. I handle my own production, mixing, and mastering.
			</p>
			<p>What I work with:</p>
			<ul>
				<li>Backend development and system design (Java, Python & Node.js)</li>
				<li>Data modeling (PostgreSQL, MongoDB, Neo4j, Qdrant, Clickhouse)</li>
				<li>Exploring AI, LLM and emerging technologies</li>
				<li>Music production across multiple instruments</li>
			</ul>
			<p>
				I'm interested in the intersection of technology and creativity, building 
				things that work well and last. My approach tends toward technical depth 
				and authentic expression over flashy presentation.
			</p>
			<p>
				You can find me on <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/lorenzo-donzelli-diaz-71796b94/">LinkedIn</a>, 
				<a href="https://www.instagram.com/loredonzdiaz/">Instagram</a>, 
				<a href="https://open.spotify.com/intl-it/artist/1tzPTUM1XKUck2s6TUh2o1">Spotify</a>, 
				or <a href="https://github.com/acjnn">GitHub</a>.
			</p>
		</main>
		<Footer />
	</body>
</html>
